                        <head>283. Minutes of Secretary of State <persName corresp="#p_KHA1">Kissinger</persName>’s Staff Meeting<note n="1" type="source" xml:id="d283fn1">Source: National Archives, <gloss target="#t_RG1">RG</gloss> 59, Transcripts of Secretary of State <persName corresp="#p_KHA1">Kissinger</persName>’s Staff Meetings,
                                1973–1977, Entry 5177, Box 6, Secretary’s Staff Meetings.
                                Secret.</note>
                        </head>
